<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>3106</hymn_number>
<author>Almondream</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 I come to you my Lord
 With my trust in you
 I believe you know my heart
 More and more than me
 Your holy spirit will touch me now
 I will never be the same again

[V2]
 Here I am at the cross
 I lay my sin down
 Here I am at the cross
 I pour out my pain

[V3]
 You my Jesus my Lord
 Suffered in my place
 Everything that today I know
 I will never have to pay again
 I will never have to pay again</lyrics>
<title>At the cross</title>
</song>